title: Nokia 's net sales 1999 to 2019
summary: In general Net sales in billion euros has rose over the Year.
Net sales in billion euros is roughly constant from 2000 to 2004, rapidly increasing from 2004 to 2007, roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, and finally slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2009.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2006 and 2007.
Maximum Net sales in billion euros, about 51.06 was reported at Year 2007
The lowest Net sales in billion euros, of value 29.37 was reported at Year 2004
